2. Asset Management
Ensure all images (splash, icons) are bundled correctly using PyInstaller's _MEIPASS temp directory logic so the installed app can find its resources.

3. Auto-Updater (Crucial for Paid Apps)
If you break something with an API change (Suno changes their API often), your users are stuck.

Implement: A simple version checker in main.py on startup.

Logic: Fetch a version.json from your GitHub. If remote_version > local_version, prompt the user to download the new installer.

